{"tid":1875212,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"召喚 捐血師！！","createTime":"2020-02-11T15:40:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T15:40:36.000Z","uid":327267,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a021125b3b472f406a82b54af9d577bae6d97a","tid":1875212,"uid":327267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T15:40:36.000Z","msg":"【#血庫告急】血庫現時所有血型的存量都處於<strong>極低水平</strong>，每天收集的血液都不足以應付每天醫院所需。<br />\n<br />\n受疫情影響，捐血<strong>人數銳減</strong>。中心過往平均每天可以收集到約700包血液，現時只收集到約300包。雖然醫院用血量因非緊急服務減少已相對下降，但基本需求，例如緊急手術、重型地貧、血癌病人的輸血治療都不能叫停。<br />\n<br />\n每種血製品都有儲存期限。例如捐出的血小板就只能夠儲存5 日，所以每一日都有足夠的捐血者，對病人至為重要。<br />\n<br />\n你可先致電全港8間捐血站，或透過手機應用程式 #HKBlood 預約捐血，方便你預算時間，亦可減少人群於捐血站內聚集。當然，中心也會做足防感染措施，竭力提供安全衛生的捐血環境。<br />\n<br />\n請即行動，捐血救人！<br />\n<br />\n捐血站地址、電話及開放時間<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/loc-all\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Floc-all&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=f5c16381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/loc-all</a><br />\n<br />\n捐血車、流動隊動向<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/mobile-schedule\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Fmobile-schedule&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=457648d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/mobile-schedule</a><br />\n<br />\n下載HKBlood 手機應用程式<br />\nIOS : <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/hk-blood/id1387423207?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fhk-blood%2Fid1387423207%3Fmt%3D8&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=4cea300c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/hk-blood/id1387423207?mt=8</a><br />\nAndroid : <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.org.ha.btsmapps&amp;rdid=hk.org.ha.btsmapps\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dhk.org.ha.btsmapps%26rdid%3Dhk.org.ha.btsmapps&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=b415a887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.org.ha.btsmapps&amp;rdid=hk.org.ha.btsmapps</a><br />\n<br />\n應對新型冠狀病毒感染的捐血預防措施<br />\n<a href=\"https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/news/news20200204\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww5.ha.org.hk%2Frcbts%2Fnews%2Fnews20200204&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=26e09ebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www5.ha.org.hk/rcbts/news/news20200204</a><br />\n<br />\n#守護傷患 #伸出援手 #捐血救人 #捐一次血救三個人 #定期捐血 #恆常捐血 #捐血 #輸血治療 #香港紅十字會輸血服務中心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/405250926171019/posts/3189398427756241/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F405250926171019%2Fposts%2F3189398427756241%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=k4A9UPuxEtmwSexvyTVA%2BdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5d08c28b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/405250926171019/posts/3189398427756241/?d=n</a>"}]}